{"tid":2321981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：輝瑞疫苗會由內地復星醫藥生產","createTime":"2020-12-12T03:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T14:13:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"06a17ad52113d91e7cfc60e53aa91d90f3e64a6d","tid":2321981,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府已向兩間供應商預購疫苗，中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指，輝瑞有份研發的疫苗會在內地由復星醫藥生產，由於疫苗要低溫存放及稀釋，預料相關工序要在醫院進行。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌：「不會在歐洲或北美訂貨，用復星生產線，來到的時間短，所以都會保到溫度，我相信政府要求復星提供雪櫃運送，到了香港再做稀釋。稀釋完要五天內用完，私家醫生唯一可以幫忙，如果科興或牛津的疫苗儲存在攝氏2度至8度，若果有需要可找私家醫生儲存。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416309&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=86d47538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416309&h=cb063302\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416309</a>"},{"pid":"db4d6d6fe446b2e37b1d4a854421b9f7f9f0fd77","tid":2321981,"uid":125385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:08:46.000Z","msg":"中国版輝瑞疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685c1d691d5dfe4db05cb70f1cf27174d1e16618","tid":2321981,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">許樹昌、梁子超講大話：屌你老母臭閪</span></span></strong>，復星一月開始每月入口過百萬德國制疫苗，點會冇時間，點會物流做唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2321878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2321878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2a9883d0a9787f7989e831f5e32a4b7d4cd7da